      "dateCreated": "2025-03-31",
      "description": "Hybrid single-cell RNA-seq analysis pipeline combining Scanpy for QC/normalization, nf-core/scdownstream for integration/clustering, and custom Scanpy scripts for automatic marker gene detection and visualization. Processes h5ad input through quality control, normalization, dimensionality reduction, clustering, and produces marker gene tables with UMAP, heatmap, and dotplot visualizations.",
